Text: Rameshwaram is the beautiful place and auspicious temple of Shiva.The temple
  visit is the most memorable part of the journey.first we need to see the crystal
  shiva lingam in the temple.after that we need to take hold dip in the sea.and then
  consecutive 22 wells water which will be bit warm and having herbal properties.after
  that we can go for main Pooja.the best thing I remembered is taking blessings from
  all your elders in your family after Pooja.mshould travel on train so we can catch
  the glimse of bridge on the sea pamban bridge.
